WEBVTT

00:59.040 --> 00:59.600
Qi Yi.

01:05.640 --> 01:06.370
You're here.

01:09.240 --> 01:11.400
I thought you weren't coming.

01:15.560 --> 01:16.890
Let's go sit over there.

01:35.200 --> 01:36.640
What you said last time,

01:37.039 --> 01:39.100
I went back and thought about it a lot.

01:39.440 --> 01:41.360
I feel I need to explain it to you.

01:43.400 --> 01:44.000
Of course,

01:44.560 --> 01:45.200
from the very beginning,

01:45.200 --> 01:47.060
I couldn't wait to get to know you.

01:47.800 --> 01:49.840
Every time you came to the imperial kiln,

01:49.840 --> 01:51.700
I volunteered to show you around.

01:56.759 --> 01:57.759
Not long after we met,

01:57.759 --> 01:59.320
I confessed to you in a rush.

02:01.280 --> 02:02.140
Did I scare you?

02:07.600 --> 02:09.600
But I'm not like this with everyone.

02:12.000 --> 02:14.200
You like history

02:15.080 --> 02:16.940
and cultural relics just like me,

02:17.160 --> 02:18.820
and you're so understanding.

02:21.520 --> 02:22.880
When I was nervous about my interview,

02:22.880 --> 02:24.740
you were the one who cheered me on.

02:24.840 --> 02:25.840
But you know what?

02:25.840 --> 02:27.840
Those aren't the reasons I like you.

02:28.760 --> 02:30.420
I can't explain why I like you.

02:31.000 --> 02:31.600
I only know

02:32.280 --> 02:33.360
that such a strong feeling

02:33.360 --> 02:34.420
is something I have

02:35.160 --> 02:36.160
never had before.

02:42.680 --> 02:43.440
I thought,

02:44.200 --> 02:47.000
since it's so rare to meet someone I like this much,

02:47.320 --> 02:49.040
if I didn't say it out loud,

02:50.440 --> 02:51.770
it would be a great pity.

02:53.160 --> 02:54.760
I didn't know how to tell you.

02:55.800 --> 02:56.530
Actually...

02:59.560 --> 03:01.960
I practiced at home for a long time that day.

03:02.760 --> 03:04.220
When I told you I liked you,

03:05.640 --> 03:06.880
I was really nervous.

03:11.080 --> 03:13.010
I can't tell exactly why I like you.

03:14.600 --> 03:15.040
I just

03:15.560 --> 03:17.600
know this feeling is quite strong.

03:21.840 --> 03:23.760
I like everything about you.

03:25.160 --> 03:26.000
Like I said,

03:28.320 --> 03:29.240
if you feel

03:29.560 --> 03:31.090
the timing isn't right yet,

03:32.200 --> 03:33.880
I can step back.

03:35.320 --> 03:35.760
We can

03:36.360 --> 03:37.690
continue to be friends.

03:40.520 --> 03:41.280
That day,

03:42.280 --> 03:42.940
when I asked

03:43.480 --> 03:45.120
if we could date,

03:47.760 --> 03:50.000
that was my truest feeling at the time.

03:58.760 --> 03:59.920
Actually,

04:01.400 --> 04:02.840
you can ask me again.

04:06.280 --> 04:07.280
Then I'll ask you,

04:09.080 --> 04:10.160
will you date me?

05:01.360 --> 05:02.560
I've told you so many times

05:02.560 --> 05:03.840
that you shouldn't eat

05:03.840 --> 05:04.800
that junk food from outside.

05:04.800 --> 05:05.800
But you just wouldn't listen.

05:05.800 --> 05:07.000
Now you know the pain.

05:07.200 --> 05:07.660
Come on,

05:07.800 --> 05:08.640
take your medicine.

05:08.640 --> 05:09.160
Come on.

05:09.640 --> 05:10.520
Slowly now.

05:15.200 --> 05:16.260
Did you swallow it?

05:16.400 --> 05:17.400
You've always been in poor health,

05:17.400 --> 05:18.440
and I'm the one who takes care of you.

05:18.440 --> 05:19.280
I know your constitution

05:19.280 --> 05:20.340
better than you do.

05:20.680 --> 05:21.760
So you have to listen to me.

05:21.760 --> 05:22.520
Got it?

05:23.480 --> 05:23.810
Let me

05:24.680 --> 05:26.080
feel if you have a fever.

05:26.280 --> 05:27.480
Let me take your temperature.

05:27.480 --> 05:28.280
No need, Mom.

05:28.280 --> 05:30.000
I'll be fine after lying down for a while.

05:30.000 --> 05:31.880
Did the whole class go out this weekend?

05:31.880 --> 05:32.760
Why did you go eat?

05:32.760 --> 05:33.560
Who was there?

05:33.760 --> 05:34.480
Aunt,

05:35.000 --> 05:37.200
my mom wants you to go for a walk with her.

05:37.400 --> 05:38.159
What walk?

05:38.159 --> 05:39.800
Your sister is in so much pain.

05:39.800 --> 05:41.320
Mom, just go.

05:42.159 --> 05:43.080
I knew it.

05:43.200 --> 05:43.920
Both of you

05:43.920 --> 05:45.320
think I'm nagging and annoying,

05:45.320 --> 05:46.780
and you won't listen to me.

05:46.880 --> 05:47.760
No.

05:49.520 --> 05:50.650
Are you really okay?

05:51.560 --> 05:52.200
Alright.

05:52.200 --> 05:53.240
I'm going out then.

05:53.240 --> 05:53.760
Let's go.

05:53.760 --> 05:55.220
Don't bother your sister.

05:55.480 --> 05:57.080
Call me if you need anything.

07:18.120 --> 07:18.650
Morning.

07:19.440 --> 07:20.000
Morning.

07:27.240 --> 07:28.770
I bought breakfast for you.

07:32.280 --> 07:34.080
Is your stomach feeling better?

07:35.240 --> 07:37.560
Didn't I tell you to rest at home a bit longer?

07:37.560 --> 07:39.690
I want to finish it as soon as possible.

07:44.400 --> 07:45.040
Cencen,

07:45.360 --> 07:46.320
you're out.

07:47.200 --> 07:50.460
Sister went to school to do extracurricular assignments.

07:53.000 --> 07:54.720
She went out early in the morning

07:54.720 --> 07:56.250
without eating breakfast.

07:56.360 --> 07:57.360
Maybe she ate out.

07:57.680 --> 07:58.400
Eating out?

07:59.400 --> 07:59.860
Well...

08:00.560 --> 08:02.080
Breakfast is ready at home, but she didn't eat here.

08:02.080 --> 08:02.740
Eating out?

08:03.000 --> 08:04.860
She only knows how to waste money.

08:06.800 --> 08:08.130
The shape is beautiful,

08:08.240 --> 08:09.700
and the color is also nice.

08:09.920 --> 08:12.380
I didn't expect Guan Lin to have such skills.

08:14.400 --> 08:15.860
I don't understand either

08:15.920 --> 08:17.920
why Mr. Wei isn't satisfied with it.

08:22.160 --> 08:23.320
Everything I do is wrong.

08:23.320 --> 08:24.180
I can see it too.

08:24.240 --> 08:25.970
You just don't plan to teach me.

08:26.320 --> 08:26.720
Right.

08:27.640 --> 08:28.520
When I die,

08:28.760 --> 08:30.490
I'd rather tear down this kiln.

08:31.200 --> 08:32.880
But I'm your only apprentice.

08:33.720 --> 08:35.850
Bullying me for being childless, huh?

08:36.000 --> 08:37.120
You think you can control me?

08:37.120 --> 08:38.440
I didn't mean that.

08:38.679 --> 08:39.320
Master.

08:39.400 --> 08:40.720
Don't call me Master.

08:40.840 --> 08:42.039
I don't deserve it.

08:42.039 --> 08:42.500
Mr. Wei.

08:43.120 --> 08:44.240
No. I don't deserve to be your master.

08:44.240 --> 08:45.680
Don't lower yourself to his level.

08:45.680 --> 08:46.920
Don't be angry, Mr. Wei.

08:46.920 --> 08:47.200
No.

08:47.200 --> 08:47.640
Let's go sit over there.

08:47.640 --> 08:49.000
Can you be reasonable, Master?

08:49.000 --> 08:50.080
Now he thinks he's so capable.

08:50.080 --> 08:50.920
Don't be angry.

08:50.920 --> 08:52.120
Please don't be angry, Mr. Wei.

08:52.120 --> 08:52.920
Please calm down.

08:52.920 --> 08:53.480
Come, come.

08:53.480 --> 08:54.880
Fine. You're so capable.

08:55.200 --> 08:55.800
Calm down.

08:56.560 --> 08:57.220
Master Wei,

08:57.440 --> 08:59.680
you've finally recovered well.

09:00.080 --> 09:01.080
Please don't get angry.

09:01.080 --> 09:02.080
Yeah, Master Wei.

09:02.160 --> 09:03.490
Please don't get angry.

09:05.800 --> 09:07.060
Why are you here again?

09:09.880 --> 09:10.540
Master Wei.

09:10.800 --> 09:11.130
Here,

09:11.440 --> 09:12.570
Mr. Wei, take a look.

09:19.480 --> 09:22.210
Look, 'Spring brings good fortune and harmony.'

09:28.800 --> 09:30.000
Good craftsmanship.

09:33.440 --> 09:36.360
I mean your restoration skills are quite good.

09:39.400 --> 09:40.460
Thank you, Mr. Wei.

09:41.040 --> 09:42.770
This porcelain made by Guan Lin

09:43.120 --> 09:45.250
was fired in the newly built Chai Kiln.

09:45.520 --> 09:47.720
It really can't compare to those fired in the old kiln.

09:47.720 --> 09:48.800
At the time, we were only focused on

09:48.800 --> 09:50.120
its shape and color,

09:51.400 --> 09:53.000
and ignored its smoothness.

09:54.600 --> 09:57.240
Young people want to run before they can walk.

09:59.600 --> 10:00.200
Forget it.

10:00.720 --> 10:01.650
You guys go back.

10:02.800 --> 10:04.330
Take this vase with you too.

10:08.040 --> 10:08.520
What?

10:10.520 --> 10:11.850
Is there anything else?

10:14.240 --> 10:15.800
How I teach my apprentices

10:16.000 --> 10:17.960
is none of your business.

10:20.760 --> 10:21.480
Brother Guan Lin.

10:21.480 --> 10:22.920
You spend all day ignoring this excellent

10:22.920 --> 10:24.960
and widely envied Wei Kiln instead of studying it.

10:24.960 --> 10:27.320
Thinking about how to fire new porcelain all day.

10:27.320 --> 10:28.600
Could it be that you're outside,

10:28.600 --> 10:30.000
using Mr. Wei's name,

10:30.160 --> 10:31.680
and secretly taking private jobs?

10:31.680 --> 10:32.680
I didn't.

10:32.880 --> 10:35.040
I have never used my master's title.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.600
Yuexin.

10:38.040 --> 10:39.840
You just complain that Mr. Wei doesn't teach you anything,

10:39.840 --> 10:41.240
and you're planning to go out and start your own business.

10:41.240 --> 10:41.680
Right?

10:41.920 --> 10:43.320
I'm not that kind of person.

10:43.320 --> 10:45.160
The day my master brought me back from the street,

10:45.160 --> 10:46.600
I swore to the God of Kilns Tong Bin

10:46.600 --> 10:48.640
that I would follow my master until I die.

10:48.640 --> 10:49.680
But you didn't expect

10:49.680 --> 10:51.840
that I could live this long, did you?

10:52.000 --> 10:53.840
Master, can we be reasonable?

10:53.840 --> 10:55.080
The new type of kiln and the Weijiayao kiln

10:55.080 --> 10:56.040
don't conflict.

10:56.040 --> 10:57.120
Now the small Chai Kiln outside,

10:57.120 --> 10:57.880
electric kilns, and microwave kilns

10:57.880 --> 11:00.540
are the choices for many small-scale products.

11:00.800 --> 11:02.600
I haven't abandoned tradition.

11:04.760 --> 11:05.360
Guan Lin.

11:07.520 --> 11:08.120
Mr. Wei.

11:08.800 --> 11:10.330
The old kiln is indeed good.

11:10.360 --> 11:11.400
But firing one kiln

11:11.400 --> 11:13.680
also consumes nearly two thousand catties of pine wood.

11:13.680 --> 11:15.520
The cost is nearly a hundred thousand.

11:15.520 --> 11:16.640
It's not that many people don't want to fire it,

11:16.640 --> 11:17.000
but

11:17.680 --> 11:19.280
they really can't afford it.

11:20.600 --> 11:22.840
The master has watched the fire for thousands of years,

11:22.840 --> 11:23.960
but when it comes to you,

11:23.960 --> 11:25.440
it becomes touching a switch.

11:25.440 --> 11:27.370
Then what's the point of using you?

11:27.600 --> 11:27.800
I...

11:27.800 --> 11:28.400
Mr. Wei.

11:29.680 --> 11:31.040
I brought some materials,

11:31.040 --> 11:31.700
take a look.

11:32.400 --> 11:33.920
In the long river of history,

11:33.920 --> 11:36.120
new types of kilns didn't come out of nowhere.

11:36.120 --> 11:37.600
Although Weijiayao is

11:37.600 --> 11:38.530
an old kiln to us,

11:38.960 --> 11:40.960
it was also an innovation back then.

11:41.720 --> 11:42.680
The development of skills

11:42.680 --> 11:45.600
will definitely bring about the development of kilns.

11:45.600 --> 11:47.930
All choices are determined by the market.

11:48.880 --> 11:50.480
So many people choosing Weijiayao

11:50.480 --> 11:51.320
has already proven

11:51.320 --> 11:52.720
its own existence value.

12:05.400 --> 12:07.860
Where is the character 'Xu' you made before?

12:08.520 --> 12:09.320
Right here.

12:10.120 --> 12:11.080
Character 'Xu'.

12:12.640 --> 12:13.900
I remember writing it.

12:14.360 --> 12:15.560
Does this look a bit like you?

12:15.560 --> 12:16.280
Like me?

12:20.080 --> 12:21.140
Maybe a little bit.

12:21.920 --> 12:23.320
Does this look even more like it?

12:23.320 --> 12:24.600
No, this one looks more like me.

12:24.600 --> 12:25.720
This one looks like it.

12:25.720 --> 12:26.520
This one looks like it.

12:26.520 --> 12:27.680
The eyes on this one are open.

12:27.680 --> 12:29.680
This one only looks like you with the eyes closed.

12:29.680 --> 12:30.120
Okay.

12:31.160 --> 12:32.490
This one looks like you.

12:34.120 --> 12:34.980
No, it doesn't.

12:37.560 --> 12:38.160
Before,

12:39.080 --> 12:40.940
you always did things I like to do.

12:42.040 --> 12:43.970
Do you have anything you like to do?

12:45.520 --> 12:46.120
You can tell me anything.

12:46.120 --> 12:47.760
Things I like to do?

12:51.320 --> 12:52.120
Claw machine.

12:53.640 --> 12:54.440
Claw machine.

12:55.160 --> 12:55.690
Is it fun?

12:55.800 --> 12:56.440
Yes, it is.

12:57.840 --> 12:58.970
Go with me next time.

13:00.680 --> 13:01.640
Let's not wait for next time.

13:01.640 --> 13:02.770
Let's go after work.

13:03.280 --> 13:03.720
Okay.

13:19.440 --> 13:21.120
Want to challenge again?

13:23.480 --> 13:25.520
That's great.

13:39.520 --> 13:40.980
My mom and aunt are at home.

13:41.120 --> 13:42.120
You should go back.

13:42.120 --> 13:43.000
I'm sorry.

13:43.000 --> 13:45.560
Am I an unqualified girlfriend?

13:45.720 --> 13:47.240
Cencen, stop looking at your phone.

13:47.240 --> 13:49.040
Go help your aunt serve the dishes.

13:49.040 --> 13:49.480
Okay.

13:51.640 --> 13:52.840
Aunt, let me help you.

13:53.320 --> 13:55.120
Okay. Take this dish in.

14:02.120 --> 14:02.680
Xiaocen.

14:03.400 --> 14:05.560
I made your favorite shredded potatoes.

14:05.560 --> 14:06.440
Thank you, Aunt.

14:06.440 --> 14:07.370
You're welcome.

14:07.880 --> 14:08.440
Want a drink?

14:08.440 --> 14:09.100
No, thanks.

14:10.440 --> 14:11.080
Here, sis.

14:26.200 --> 14:26.840
Master,

14:27.800 --> 14:30.000
are you sure you want to take this order?

14:30.200 --> 14:31.840
I looked at this batch of porcelain.

14:31.840 --> 14:33.680
It'll take at least two or three days to fire the kiln.

14:33.680 --> 14:34.800
I'm worried about your health.

14:34.800 --> 14:36.320
What if something happens...

14:36.320 --> 14:38.120
You think I can't do it?

14:38.640 --> 14:39.520
No, Master.

14:40.680 --> 14:42.840
Do you think it's possible

14:43.240 --> 14:43.760
that

14:44.280 --> 14:45.140
I do the firing,

14:45.360 --> 14:45.800
and you

14:45.960 --> 14:47.520
supervise and guide me from the side?

14:47.520 --> 14:47.920
You...

14:47.920 --> 14:49.240
You do the firing?

14:49.920 --> 14:50.360
Yeah.

14:50.800 --> 14:53.130
Have you completed your apprenticeship?

14:53.280 --> 14:53.880
Enough.

14:54.400 --> 14:55.240
This order,

14:55.680 --> 14:56.740
I've decided on it.

14:56.800 --> 14:57.930
I have the final say.

14:58.520 --> 14:58.960
Go.

15:03.560 --> 15:04.960
Fortunately,

15:05.280 --> 15:06.560
I came to Jingdezhen.

15:07.920 --> 15:08.880
And luckily,

15:09.960 --> 15:12.160
I came to Fuliang because of Weijiayao.

15:14.120 --> 15:16.360
Otherwise, I wouldn't have seen such beautiful scenery.

15:16.360 --> 15:17.760
During the Tang Dynasty,

15:17.880 --> 15:20.280
Fuliang became the national porcelain-making center.

15:20.280 --> 15:21.560
It's said that at that time,

15:21.560 --> 15:23.200
craftsmen gathered from everywhere,

15:23.200 --> 15:25.200
and kiln fires burned day and night.

15:25.520 --> 15:26.360
Yaoli's glaze

15:26.880 --> 15:28.240
and Fuliang's Kaolin Clay

15:28.240 --> 15:29.440
were discovered here

15:30.160 --> 15:31.620
and fired into porcelain.

15:32.960 --> 15:33.800
Xu Xiao.

15:35.520 --> 15:37.280
Sometimes I feel like

15:37.760 --> 15:39.420
you are someone from the past.

15:42.120 --> 15:45.320
Haven't you ever thought about going out to see the world?

15:45.880 --> 15:46.410
Where to?

15:49.200 --> 15:50.080
Like,

15:50.720 --> 15:51.560
my hometown.

15:52.480 --> 15:53.080
Of course.

15:55.560 --> 15:56.480
I've always wanted to go

15:56.480 --> 15:58.080
to the place where you grew up

15:58.320 --> 15:59.120
to take a look.

16:01.680 --> 16:02.720
At first,

16:03.400 --> 16:04.920
when I came to Jingdezhen,

16:05.560 --> 16:07.040
I wasn't quite used to it.

16:07.640 --> 16:08.560
First,

16:09.040 --> 16:11.480
I was mad at myself for not doing well in the exams.

16:11.480 --> 16:12.120
Second,

16:12.720 --> 16:15.780
this place is indeed quite different from my hometown.

16:15.960 --> 16:16.520
Really.

16:17.680 --> 16:18.920
When school was about to start,

16:18.920 --> 16:20.250
I kept dragging my feet.

16:20.880 --> 16:23.520
But my mom had already arranged everything for me.

16:23.520 --> 16:25.560
But now I really like it here.

16:26.480 --> 16:27.810
I've fallen in love with

16:28.320 --> 16:30.250
every blade of grass and tree here.

16:32.000 --> 16:33.880
And everyone here.

17:10.040 --> 17:10.640
I'm sorry.

17:11.720 --> 17:12.560
I didn't know.

17:16.599 --> 17:17.119
I...

18:18.000 --> 18:18.530
Let's go.

18:31.840 --> 18:32.170
Here,

18:34.160 --> 18:34.880
it's wrong,

18:35.560 --> 18:36.280
got it?

18:37.400 --> 18:39.440
Practice this part again.

18:40.040 --> 18:40.960
Xiaocen.

18:42.080 --> 18:43.840
Why are you back so late again?

18:45.800 --> 18:48.160
I went to Weijiayao.

18:48.320 --> 18:49.720
Weijiayao is so far away.

18:50.080 --> 18:51.600
Why did the professors assign you

18:51.600 --> 18:53.880
so many extracurricular activities recently?

18:53.880 --> 18:55.840
It's good to take practical classes.

18:55.840 --> 18:56.680
You can make some

18:56.680 --> 18:57.880
friends with common interests.

18:57.880 --> 18:58.840
Isn't that nice?

18:59.360 --> 19:00.720
Having enough credits is fine.

19:00.720 --> 19:02.280
Why do you need so many credits?

19:02.280 --> 19:03.320
But Aunt,

19:03.960 --> 19:05.840
you didn't demand that of me.

19:07.240 --> 19:09.440
Can you compare yourself to your sister now?

19:09.440 --> 19:11.680
Every single point matters to you right now.

19:11.680 --> 19:13.410
Don't find your aunt annoying.

19:14.240 --> 19:16.320
Look, are you learning this instrument

19:16.320 --> 19:17.920
just to avoid doing exercises?

19:17.920 --> 19:19.280
I'm telling you, your mom spoils you,

19:19.280 --> 19:20.400
but Aunt won't.

19:21.160 --> 19:22.280
Alright, Sis.

19:22.280 --> 19:24.520
That's all based on your experience.

19:24.920 --> 19:26.560
Xiaoxing, hurry up and practice.

19:26.560 --> 19:27.680
Once you're done, go inside and do your test papers.

19:27.680 --> 19:29.120
I still have to do them?

19:29.120 --> 19:29.840
Of course.

19:31.840 --> 19:32.440
Cencen.

19:33.080 --> 19:35.200
Your studies have been too heavy lately.

19:35.200 --> 19:36.530
Remember what Mom said.

19:36.680 --> 19:38.680
Trading your health for grades

19:38.760 --> 19:39.760
is never worth it.

19:39.880 --> 19:41.740
Mom, I'm feeling much better now.

19:42.000 --> 19:44.200
And Jingdezhen has beautiful scenery.

19:45.200 --> 19:46.880
The doctor even said I can stop my medication.

19:46.880 --> 19:47.680
Right, Sis.

19:47.680 --> 19:49.210
The air here is really good.

19:50.120 --> 19:51.360
And for someone

19:51.360 --> 19:52.960
to find a major they like

19:52.960 --> 19:54.680
is not an easy thing.

19:54.920 --> 19:55.960
Many people even now

19:55.960 --> 19:57.690
don't have a direction in life.

19:57.800 --> 19:59.640
Final exams are starting soon.

19:59.720 --> 20:01.400
Just stay home and read.

20:01.640 --> 20:02.440
Go out less.

20:02.880 --> 20:03.680
Got it.

20:12.160 --> 20:12.620
Sister,

20:13.080 --> 20:14.540
why aren't you asleep yet?

20:15.680 --> 20:16.480
I can't sleep.

20:17.040 --> 20:17.760
What's up?

20:19.920 --> 20:20.720
What's wrong?

20:25.600 --> 20:26.840
Look at our Cencen.

20:27.480 --> 20:29.520
She either stays out all day

20:29.840 --> 20:32.040
or comes home and stays up late reading.

20:32.720 --> 20:34.780
I'm really worried about her health.

20:38.560 --> 20:39.080
Sister,

20:39.200 --> 20:41.120
can you look after her forever?

20:42.600 --> 20:43.840
I don't know why,

20:43.880 --> 20:46.280
but I've been feeling a bit anxious lately.

20:46.560 --> 20:47.720
How could you not be?

20:47.760 --> 20:49.160
You worry too much.

20:49.600 --> 20:50.360
Look here,

20:50.520 --> 20:52.450
you have a white hair sticking out.

20:53.120 --> 20:53.920
Where?

20:54.120 --> 20:54.780
Right here.

20:54.840 --> 20:55.920
Pluck it out for me.

20:56.040 --> 20:56.640
White hairs.

20:56.640 --> 20:58.160
You can't pluck them, I'm telling you.

20:58.160 --> 21:00.820
The more you pluck, the more will grow, you know?

21:11.680 --> 21:14.520
Master Wei, please preside over the lighting ceremony.

21:14.520 --> 21:15.040
Please.

21:18.320 --> 21:20.160
Pay respects to the Kiln God.

21:42.800 --> 21:46.880
The kiln ancestors soar to the sky, and the cranes wander.

21:47.240 --> 21:48.770
Protect our kiln industry,

21:49.160 --> 21:51.960
to prosper forever.

21:53.520 --> 21:54.850
Pay respects to heaven.

21:56.760 --> 21:58.320
Pay respects to earth.

22:00.760 --> 22:03.320
Pay respects to the Kiln God.

22:30.240 --> 22:31.480
Push it in. Push it in.

22:31.800 --> 22:33.060
Be careful. Push it in.

22:33.680 --> 22:34.540
Lao Chen, come.

22:35.160 --> 22:35.800
Lend a hand.

22:35.800 --> 22:36.200
Come, come.

22:36.200 --> 22:36.560
Come.

22:36.560 --> 22:37.720
Get this ready.

22:41.160 --> 22:42.560
Put the wet ones aside.

22:42.560 --> 22:43.560
Don't put them in.

22:44.080 --> 22:45.960
Even out the big pieces.

22:46.040 --> 22:46.520
Okay.

22:46.520 --> 22:47.200
Put it over there.

22:47.200 --> 22:48.000
Give me a hand.

22:54.320 --> 22:55.120
Add firewood.

22:55.720 --> 22:56.320
Coming.

22:56.520 --> 22:57.080
Come.

22:59.200 --> 23:00.240
Level it out.

23:00.840 --> 23:02.000
Watch the vent.

23:16.520 --> 23:17.040
Master,

23:17.520 --> 23:18.320
what's wrong?

23:19.040 --> 23:19.840
I'm here.

23:21.400 --> 23:23.600
I'm fine. I just dozed off.

23:23.760 --> 23:24.840
Don't make a fuss.

23:25.040 --> 23:25.800
Are you sure you're okay?

23:25.800 --> 23:26.560
I'm fine.

23:26.560 --> 23:27.000
Okay.

23:59.160 --> 24:00.220
Alright, alright.

24:00.520 --> 24:01.200
You guys,

24:01.920 --> 24:02.600
you guys,

24:02.920 --> 24:04.080
go back and get some rest.

24:04.080 --> 24:05.160
Okay, okay.

24:06.680 --> 24:07.640
Everyone, go back.

24:07.640 --> 24:09.080
Thanks for your hard work, guys.

24:09.080 --> 24:09.680
It's fine.

24:09.880 --> 24:10.410
Guan Lin,

24:11.760 --> 24:12.640
you stay.

24:13.400 --> 24:14.240
Keep watch.

24:15.240 --> 24:15.840
Hurry up.

24:29.880 --> 24:31.540
Do you want to rest a bit later?

24:31.960 --> 24:33.280
The smoke is heavy inside.

24:33.280 --> 24:34.410
You don't look well.

24:35.000 --> 24:36.320
I can't bear to rest.

24:36.760 --> 24:38.320
All the changes in the kiln right now

24:38.320 --> 24:39.760
feel so magical to me.

24:40.160 --> 24:42.020
The pine resin emitted by the wood

24:42.160 --> 24:43.320
and the fine moisture in the kiln

24:43.320 --> 24:44.280
are combining,

24:45.240 --> 24:47.080
soaking into the porcelain body.

24:47.080 --> 24:47.440
Here.

24:47.760 --> 24:49.720
I can't help but start imagining

24:50.440 --> 24:52.440
what the natural pine ash glaze

24:52.440 --> 24:53.300
will look like.

24:53.640 --> 24:55.400
That's why the experienced masters know

24:55.400 --> 24:56.480
that opening the kiln every time

24:56.480 --> 24:58.140
brings a different surprise.

24:59.000 --> 24:59.960
Or maybe a scare.

25:02.400 --> 25:03.000
Let's eat.

25:05.680 --> 25:06.480
The food is ready.

25:06.480 --> 25:07.000
Yeah.

25:07.680 --> 25:08.210
Sit down.

25:09.240 --> 25:09.800
I'm starving.

25:09.800 --> 25:10.760
Mr. Wei isn't here yet.

25:10.760 --> 25:12.420
He's still watching the kiln.

25:15.320 --> 25:16.380
Where is my master?

25:16.880 --> 25:18.240
He's still watching the kiln.

25:18.240 --> 25:19.170
It's time to eat!

25:20.600 --> 25:22.600
Master, whenever it's mealtime...

25:23.080 --> 25:23.680
Master.

25:24.960 --> 25:25.440
Master.

25:28.400 --> 25:29.000
Master.

25:29.000 --> 25:29.560
Mr. Wei.

25:29.680 --> 25:30.080
Mr. Wei.

25:30.080 --> 25:30.720
Call an ambulance.

25:30.720 --> 25:31.200
Mr. Wei.

25:31.320 --> 25:31.960
Mr. Wei.

25:32.520 --> 25:33.080
How is he?

25:35.720 --> 25:36.600
How is Mr. Wei?

25:37.200 --> 25:38.800
Was he still firing the kiln?

25:39.360 --> 25:39.840
Yes.

25:40.880 --> 25:43.080
We advised him to come to the hospital for treatment long ago.

25:43.080 --> 25:44.520
But he just wouldn't listen.

25:44.520 --> 25:46.720
He didn't even let us tell you the truth.

25:47.720 --> 25:48.720
Mr. Wei,

25:51.800 --> 25:52.330
Mr. Guan.

25:52.760 --> 25:53.290
Mr. Guan,

25:54.360 --> 25:55.360
look at this fire.

25:55.400 --> 25:56.600
Should we control it?

25:58.480 --> 25:59.240
Okay.

26:00.040 --> 26:00.720
Mr. Guan,

26:01.600 --> 26:02.930
it rained a few days ago.

26:02.960 --> 26:04.360
Look at these pieces of pine.

26:04.360 --> 26:06.220
Is the moisture content too high?

26:06.760 --> 26:07.160
Yes,

26:07.680 --> 26:08.280
it is.

26:09.840 --> 26:12.080
Mr. Wei's cancer worsened a long time ago.

26:12.080 --> 26:13.640
Even though he looks happy all day,

26:13.640 --> 26:15.560
he's actually just pushing through.

26:15.560 --> 26:17.760
He also said his apprentices couldn't know.

26:17.760 --> 26:18.800
If they found out,

26:19.080 --> 26:20.840
they wouldn't focus on learning.

26:20.840 --> 26:22.280
Then this time, it's because...

26:22.280 --> 26:23.560
The medication I gave him

26:23.560 --> 26:25.120
is already at the maximum dosage.

26:25.120 --> 26:25.760
Normally,

26:26.160 --> 26:27.960
just enduring the physical pain

26:28.520 --> 26:30.080
drains most of his energy.

26:31.120 --> 26:33.320
Given his current physical condition,

26:33.520 --> 26:34.850
how can he fire the kiln?

26:35.120 --> 26:36.400
Isn't it just nonsense?
